>Giro d’Italia 2025: Live UK TV and streaming times</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/05/GettyImages-2151874952-min-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/05/GettyImages-2151874952-min-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/05/GettyImages-2151874952-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/05/GettyImages-2151874952-min-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/05/GettyImages-2151874952-min-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/05/GettyImages-2151874952-min-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/05/GettyImages-2151874952-min-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/05/GettyImages-2151874952-min-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/05/GettyImages-2151874952-min-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/05/GettyImages-2151874952-min-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/05/GettyImages-2151874952-min-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Dario Belingheri/Getty Images</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>All times and channels are subject to change and listed in BST. Times will be updated once more details are given.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Stage 1: Friday 9th May</h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>TNT Sports 1 and 3, Discovery+:</strong> 12:00-17:00</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h4>Stage 2: Saturday 10th May</h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>TNT Sports 3, Discovery+:</strong> 12:00-17:00</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h4>Stage 3: Sunday 11th May</h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>TNT Sports 3, Discovery+:</strong> 12:00-17:00</li>